# Client-Side Todo List Application

## 📌 Project Objective
The objective of this project is to build a responsive Todo List application that runs completely in the browser. It allows users to manage their daily tasks efficiently without using any database.

---

## 📖 Project Description
This Todo List application enables users to add, complete, and delete tasks.  
All tasks are stored using **localStorage**, which ensures that the tasks remain saved even after refreshing or reopening the browser.

The application also includes filters to view:
- All tasks
- Active tasks
- Completed tasks

---

## 🛠 Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- Browser LocalStorage

---

## ⚙️ Setup Instructions
1. Download or clone the project.
2. Open the project folder.
3. Double-click the **index.html** file.
4. The Todo application will open in your browser.

No installation or server is required.

---

## ✨ Features
- Add new tasks
- Mark tasks as completed
- Delete tasks
- Save tasks using localStorage
- Filter tasks (All / Active / Completed)
- Responsive design for mobile and desktop

